{"word":"ὑπακούω","slug":"ὑπακούω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ὑπαϰούω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὑπό\">ὑπό</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀκούω\">ἀκούω</a></el>] ‘be in compliance’, <b>obey <a href='B:470 8:7'>Mt 8:7</a>; <a href='B:480 1:27'>Mk 1:27</a>; <a href='B:490 17:6'>Lk 17:6</a>; <a href='B:510 6:7'>Ac 6:7</a>; <a href='B:520 6:12'>Ro 6:12</a>, <a href='B:520 6:16'>16</a>; <a href='B:560 6:1'>Eph 6:1</a>, <a href='B:560 6:5'>5</a>; <a href='B:570 2:12'>Phil 2:12</a>; <a href='B:580 3:20'>Col 3:20</a>; <a href='B:600 3:14'>2 Th 3:14</a>; <a href='B:650 11:8'>Hb 11:8</a>; <a href='B:670 3:6'>1 Pt 3:6</a>.—</b>W. focus on action in response to a summons signalled by a knock on the door <b>answer <a href='B:510 12:13'>Ac 12:13</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ὑπακοή\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ὕπανδρος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}